{
  "stem": "9943.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But that's what I decided that I want to be-- I want to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And, of course, in those years, you know, one did not so easily use women as doctors to begin with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Like, for example, in Warsaw, women-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a woman was not a general practitioner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "A woman was not a surgeon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In, in Warsaw, there were two women surgeons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "One was the wife of the Professor [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the other was my partner that-- that I mentioned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Mira ?] was her name, from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was thinking that we should go away somewhere because he could not find a job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was approaching a specialization.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in my field, the field that I-- that I selected, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which was a combination of pediatrics with neurology, I probably felt that I would-- that I would get enough work.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And besides, the minute I graduated, I was talking about my graduation, that Zabludowska-- Gina, that was my friend-- her father had high blood pressure.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the day I got my degree, he wanted me to be his doctor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's probably why I was going to talk about them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I became his doctor right after I just got officially [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] graduated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- he wanted me to be his-- people had confidence in me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Come to say it in a brief sentence, for some reason, people had confidence in me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The same thing happened with this-- with-- where my-- if I gave an ad in the paper that I'm giving lessons.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anytime that I went to see the family, they, they hired me.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
